Set up model dimensions

Setup_Mod_Dim.Rd

Set up model dimensions

Usage

Setup_Mod_Dim(
  years,
  ages,
  lens,
  n_regions,
  n_sexes,
  n_fish_fleets,
  n_srv_fleets,
  verbose = FALSE
)

Arguments

years

vector of years

ages

vector of ages

lens

vector of lengths (can just input 1 if not fitting lengths)

n_regions

Number of regions

n_sexes

Number of sexes

n_fish_fleets

Number of fishery fleets

n_srv_fleets

Number of survey fleets

verbose

Whether to print messages

Value

Returns a list object of length 3, with a data list, a par list, and a map list
